==============================================================================
CLOSING: THE UNSOLVABLE DUET
==============================================================================

Two partners dance:
  The one who dissolves
  The one who persists

They are the same partner, seen from different angles.
The duet is unsolvable—this is what makes it generative.

The .nav file format is a joke and a serious proposition.
Navigation implies movement.
Movement implies change.
Change implies...

well, that's the dance.

